<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.147in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Armpositie
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Weerstand (25 &#176;C (77 &#176;F))
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
MAX COOL [a]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Ong. 2,4 k&#937;
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
MAX HOT [b]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Ong. 4,8 k&#937;
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Meet met een ohmmeter de weerstand tussen aansluitklemmen &#34;1&#34; en &#34;3&#34;.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Vervang de stelmotor van de temperatuurregeling als het controleresultaat niet met de voorgeschreven waarden overeenstemt.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Weerstand van de stelmotor van de temperatuurregeling (totale weerstand)
</title>
<ptxt>
6 k&#937;
</ptxt>
